name: Breaking on my Mind #2
description:
Breaking on my Mind #2

When I asked my friend P.E on the right to perform a breaking move, "yo! do the 2000, I'll take a picture", Ali on the left knew I was shooting on film, and he jumped into my framing at the very last second.

I was mad at him "Why you did that for? you know it's film!"

"ahah I wanted to show the wind he's creating by spinning", Ali said.

I didn't want to take another shot, I was so pissed... and guess what, the more I look at it, the more I like it. He gave me a better story for this picture.

When you plan to stage some picture, let your friend ruin it!

--
Breaking is the original name of Breakdance, dancers are called b-boy and b-girl, it goes for Break-Boy and Break-Girl because they dance on the break of the songs. This culture made me who I am today, welcome to the breaking culture.

Alexandre Desane.
